19:55.527 --> 19:58.655
- You!
- Homer, thank God. You gotta help me here.

19:58.764 --> 20:03.360
Oh, I'll help you.
Help you die! Waaah!

20:03.468 --> 20:06.437
All right, that's it.
You're goir down, pal.

